ActConvention for the Conservation of Salmon in the North Atlantic Ocean
PrecisAppointment of CARL McLEAN of Happy Valley-Goose Bay, Newfoundland and Labrador, for a term of two years, to be a Canadian representative to the Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; to the North American Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; effective March 1, 2014, in the place of Serge Tremblay, whose term will expire.
